                    <span id="c-450221366" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-450221366" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="450221366">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2521369/">李大卫</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2011-10-25</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">既然强调将being译作“是”，何以不将ontology译作“是学”，而是旧译“本体论”？</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="446685816">
        <div class="comment">
